<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>TecHCD: Reset Your Password</title>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      font-family: Bahnschrift, 'DIN Alternate', 'Franklin Gothic Medium',
        'Nimbus Sans Narrow', sans-serif-condensed, sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.1;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    "
  >
    <table style="margin-top: 1em; width: 100%">
      <tr style="vertical-align: bottom">
        <td>
          <h1 style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600">Reset Your Password</h1>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div style="margin-left: auto; width: 64px; height: 64px">
            <img
              src="https://techcd.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/TECHCD_LOGO.png"
              alt="TecHCD Studios Logo"
              width="100%"
              height="100%"
              style="object-fit: contain; object-position: center"
            />
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)" />

    <p>Hi <%= firstName %>,</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset the password for your TecHCD account.</p>
    <p>Click the link below to create a new password:</p>

    <a
      href="<%= resetLink %>"
      style="
        display: block;
        width: fit-content;
        margin: 1em 0;
        padding: 0.8em 2.4em;
        background-color: #0084f0;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 0.3em;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
        font-family: monospace;
        font-size: 1.1em;
      "
    >
      Reset Your Password
    </a>

    <p>
      If the above link doesn't work, copy and paste the following in your
      browser
    </p>

    <div style="background-color: rgba(0, 132, 240, 0.051); padding: 1em">
      <a
        href="<%= resetLink %>"
        style="
          display: block;
          color: #0084f0;
          overflow: hidden;
          text-overflow: ellipsis;
        "
      >
        <%= resetLink %>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p>
      This password reset link will expire in 1 hour for your security.If you
      didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>

    <p>
      Best regards, <br />
      The TecHCD Team.
    </p>

    <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)" />
    <p style="opacity: 0.4; font-size: 0.8em">Â© 2025 TecHCD</p>
  </body>
</html>
